lass%3D%22ext-hanging-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20sons%20of%20Asaph%2C%20there%20were%20Zaccur%2C%20Joseph%2C%20Nethaniah%2C%20and%20Asarelah.%20They%20worked%20under%20the%20direction%20of%20their%20father%2C%20Asaph%2C%20who%20proclaimed%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20messages%20by%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_25_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20sons%20of%20Jeduthun%2C%20there%20were%20Gedaliah%2C%20Zeri%2C%20Jeshaiah%2C%20Shimei%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E25%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20one%20Hebrew%20manuscript%20and%20some%20Greek%20manuscripts%20(see%20also%2025%3A17)%3B%20most%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%20lack%20%3Cem%3EShimei.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hashabiah%2C%20and%20Mattithiah%2C%20six%20in%20all.%20They%20worked%20under%20the%20direction%20of%20their%20father%2C%20Jeduthun%2C%20who%20proclaimed%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20messages%20to%20the%20accompaniment%20of%20the%20lyre%2C%20offering%20thanks%20and%20praise%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_25_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2225%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20sons%20of%20Heman%2C%20there%20were%20Bukkiah%2C%20Mattaniah%2C%20Uzziel%2C%20Shubael%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E25%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EShebuel%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Shubael%3B%20compare%2025%3A20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Jerimoth%2C%20Hananiah%2C%20Hanani%2C%20Eliathah%2C%20Giddalti%2C%20Romamti-ezer%2C%20Joshbekashah%2C%20Mallothi%2C%20Hothir%2C%20and%20Mahazioth.%20%3Cverse_expo